Our California-cool Montecito project blends indoor-outdoor living seamlessly + we couldn’t be more pleased to finally share all its beauty! With an amazing team and stunning views, you won’t want to miss this! Check out @thehavenlist for more on this beautiful home! #brandonarchitects

___________________________
Builder: @rdm_general_contractors 
Interior: @brookewagnerdesign 
Landscape Design: @gardenstudiodesign 
Lens: @ryanbcreative
